 scen_overview {
  coords 4589.086 149.487 7155.39
  m_sTitle "Scenario Overview"
  m_sTextData "A downed pilot must link up with the local civilian population and West German Militia units to recover intelligence from his copilot and escape and evade a soviet platoon."
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
 }
 Civ {
  coords 4457.394 148.401 6950.732
  m_sTitle "Situation "
  m_sTextData "You are civilian residents of recently occupied West Germany. Last week Soviet forces came across the border and pushed NATO forces back. Until now, your homes have been unaffected by the war. "\
  ""\
  "Unfortunately, some local kids have reported that two NATO pilots have ejected right over your home town of Montignac. One is confirmed dead, and was reportedly in possession of some very important looking intel documents that are bright red."\
  ""\
  "The other survived the landing, and is somewhere nearby."\
  ""\
  "Your friend who was totally going to join the army but didn't has also said he thinks there will probably be some local militia units trying to find the pilot and get him out of dodge before the Soviets arrive."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "CIV"
  }
 }
 miss_notes {
  coords 5829.806 31.576 4226.425
  m_sTitle "Mission Notes"
  m_sTextData "Time Limit: None"\
  ""\
  "Slot Pilot and 1 Civilian minimum."\
  "3:1 OPFOR:INDFOR"\
  ""\
  "OPFOR Victory: US Pilot is killed and Soviets extract with intel OR"\
  "US Pilot and 100% of West German Militia are killed."\
  ""\
  "Blufor/Indfor Victory: US Pilot extracts WITH intel OR"\
  "90% of Soviets are killed."\
  ""\
  "If neither victory condition is met, winner is the faction holding the intel."\
  "(Blu, Civ and Ind are aligned)"\
  ""
  m_bEmptyFactionVisibility 1
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 Civ2 {
  coords 3506.51 85.764 6753.631
  m_sTitle "Mission"
  m_sTextData "Your first priority is to survive."\
  ""\
  "If safe to do so, you should covertly try to help link the downed pilot with any West German Militia units that arrive in town. The sooner the pilot is gone, the sooner you can return to avoiding the attention of Soviet forces."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "CIV"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 Civ3 {
  coords 3435.473 58.241 6837.324
  m_sTitle "Execution"
