  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "CIV"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 Civ4 {
  coords 3378.885 69.342 6737.746
  m_sTitle "Service and Support"
  m_sTextData "You have local vehicles and that is all."\
  ""\
  "You may choose to arm yourself for the purpose of self defense IF and only IF you witness soviet forces executing civilians and believe your life to be in imminent danger."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "CIV"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 Civ5 {
  coords 3436.518 56.834 6847.389
  m_sTitle "Mission Maker's Intent"
  m_sTextData "Civilians are meant to secretly help Blufor and Indfor find each other and complete their objectives since they can blend in with local population."\
  ""\
  "If Soviets get trigger happy, civilians can arm themselves BUT they will become valid targets for Soviets at that point and won't be able to help Blufor or Indfor complete their objectives."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "CIV"
  }
  m_iOrder 4
 }
 Ind {
  coords 4472.357 122.409 8188.374
  m_sTitle "Situation"
  m_sTextData "You are a West German Militia unit behind enemy lines in recently occupied West Germany. Last week Soviet forces came across the border and pushed NATO forces back. Until now, your task has been to lay low and wait for orders."\
  ""\
  "Moments ago, a NATO twin seater jet crashed and burned on it's way to a target somewhere east of here. Both pilots ejected over the town of Montignac."\
  ""\
  "Your cell leader has decided to find those pilots before the Soviets do. "
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRA"
  }
 }
 Ind2 {
  coords 4501.642 132.105 7484.966
  m_sTitle "Situation Enemy"
  m_sTextData "There is a smashed up motor rifle battalion stationed in Villeneuve for repairs, among other rear echelon units."\
  "It's likely they have at least one platoon to spare and it's probably on it's way to Montignac as we speak."\
  ""\
  "Expect BTR mounted troops with AK-74s, RPGs and RPKs."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRA"
  }
  m_iOrder 1
 }
 Ind3 {
  coords 4501.642 132.105 7484.966
  m_sTitle "Situation Friendly"
  m_sTextData "You have 10 men, lightly armed with mismatched small arms including one LMG and one GPMG. "\
  "You have no anti-armor capability. You are at Grid 051 070."
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRA"
  }
  m_iOrder 2
 }
 Ind4 {
  coords 4501.642 132.105 7484.966
  m_sTitle "Situation Civilian"
  m_sTextData "The town of Montignac has been largely bypassed and untouched during the opening phases of the war so civilian activity will be high."\
  "They hate the Soviets as much as we do, so we don't expect collaborators or sympathizers, but we can't rule it out either."\
  ""\
  "You should seek out anyone who may have information about the pilot's whereabouts."\
  ""\
  "Under no circumstances should you give them any weapons or military materiel. Doing so could turn the entire town into a target for Soviet reprisals."\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "GC_IRA"
  }
  m_iOrder 3
 }
 Ind5 {
  coords 4501.642 132.105 7484.966
  m_sTitle "Mission"
